commit.message:
Set up CI using GitHub Actions

This ports our Travis CI setup to GitHub Actions, and also adds CI for
Python 3.8 and 3.9. 3.10 was not added as it is broken due to deprecated
'#' formats. 3.4 was dropped as it's not available on Ubuntu 20.04.

'#' formats. 3.4 was dropped as it's not available on Ubuntu 20.04.
